<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-04-15T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-04-15T16:00:00-05:00" n="767" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d767">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/4–1647: Telegram</note>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Smith</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                        </hi>
                    </head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-04-16T00:00:00+03:00">April 16,
                                1947—midnight</date>.<lb/>[Received April 17—2:15 a.m.]</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>1411. <hi rend="smallcaps">Kosmos</hi> 47. From Marshall: My <hi rend="smallcaps">Kosmos</hi> 43<note n="46" xml:id="d767fn1">
                            <hi rend="italic">Supra</hi>.</note> on abandonment of ammunition
                        refers. Change last paragraph as follows:</p>
                    <p>(<hi rend="italic">a</hi>) Insert after fourth word the phrase “if inquiry is
                        made” and (<hi rend="italic">b</hi>) delete all words after “national
                        government”.</p>
                    <p>I do not want a press release and believe our reply in event question arises
                        should be forceful and direct. [Marshall]</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Smith</hi>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>